About this hotel

Featuring traditional decor with intricate geometric patterns, this cozy guesthouse in the citys medieval walled medina is 7 minutes' walk from Jemaa El Fna, a bustling square and marketplace, and 6 km from Marrakesh Menara Airport.

Check-in time: 2:00 PM
Check-out time: 12:00 PM

  • Wi-Fifree
  • Air conditioning
  • Airport shuttle

    Medina

    Hammam bath houses and covered spice and textile souks line the maze of cobblestoned lanes in the Medina, which occupies Marrakeshs original fortified citadel. At night, Jemaa el-Fna square teems with snake charmers, folk dancers, and street food vendors serving all manner of food. Bahia Palace and Le Jardin Secret are 19th-century complexes open to the public, with ornate courtyards, mosaics, and gardens.

    About this hotel

    Featuring traditional decor with intricate geometric patterns, this cozy guesthouse in the citys medieval walled medina is 7 minutes' walk from Jemaa El Fna, a bustling square and marketplace, and 6 km from Marrakesh Menara Airport.

    The warm, down-to-earth rooms come with satellite TV, air-conditioning and en suite bathrooms. Wi-Fi is available.

    Complimentary breakfast is served on a rooftop terrace; other meals are offered at additional cost. There's also a lounge with a canvas roof and sides.
